This token commemorates a Zora Zine Print Issue 001 NFT that was redeemed for a physical copy of the issue.
This token cannot be redeemed for the physical issue and serves solely as an eternal memento.

Zora Zine Print Issue 001 is a 250-page magazine featuring work from over 60 contributors from various generations of internet builders.
Published by Actual Source, produced by Zora.
